import React, { Component } from 'react'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'


class App extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col md={4}>1</Col>
                    <Col md={4}>2</Col>
                    <Col md={4}>3</Col>
                </Row>
                <Row>
                    <Col md={4}>1</Col>
                    <Col md={4}>2</Col>
                    <Col md={4}>3</Col>
                </Row>
                <Row>
                    <Col md={8}>1</Col>
                    <Col md={4}>2</Col>
                </Row>




            </Container>
        )
    }
}

export default App
